data.description: HIGHLY MOTIVATED SELLERS! Edmond school district, this Beautiful Home has a Large back yard, offers 3-bedroom, bonus room upstairs, 2 and a half baths, 3 car garage. The Master SUITE boasts an Oversized closet and huge bathroom. Jack and Jill bedrooms with nice size bath room.
